  "block_name": "play_pattern_ai_at_current_location_simple2",
  "content": "<table>\n\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"width: 40%\"><img src=\"https://images.code.org/27fc714cd6c35ed152e8bf84c1d35726-Screenshot 2024-11-07 at 9.17.17 PM.png\"></td>\n    <td style=\"width: 60%; padding: 10px;\">\n      You can use AI (Artificial Intelligence) to generate new beats!\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"width: 40%\"><img src=\"https://images.code.org/a157f9ba40cf7f33fcf8fac6745c1479-music-panels-8-2.gif\"></td>\n    <td style=\"width: 60%; padding: 10px;\">\n      Start by adding four of your own beats. \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"width: 40%\"><img src=\"https://images.code.org/f3e5aa0f76e803c54e8e36e73855f789-music-panels-8-3-b.gif\"></td>\n    <td style=\"width: 60%; padding: 10px;\">\n      A.I. will generate more beats based on what you started. \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"width: 40%\"><img src=\"https://images.code.org/8a7978d2f7ee428b65717debb24f58fc-music-panels-10-2-b.gif\"></td>\n    <td style=\"width: 60%; padding: 10px;\">\n      You can also change A.I.'s temperature to make its predictions more adventurous. \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"width: 40%\"><img src=\"https://images.code.org/b8bcf8ce4a930b29f639befa6b6e6032-music-panels-10-3-b.gif\"></td>\n    <td style=\"width: 60%; padding: 10px;\">\n      A low temperature will make A.I. stay close to what you started with. <br />\n\t  A high temperature will make A.I. generate more surprising sounds.\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n</table>    \n\n<hr />\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;\">Play AI Drums Interface</p>\n\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; width: 100%; margin-top: 10px\">\n    <!-- Section 1 -->\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; width: 100%;\">\n        <img src=\"https://images.code.org/35f5cac92bef876d6c81b8dce447702f-Screenshot 2025-05-22 143517.png\" \n             alt=\"Interface for Play AI Drums block\" \n             style=\"width: 30%; border-radius: 10px; margin: 0px 20px 20px 0px;\">\n        <div>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.2; margin: 5px 0;\">\n                <span style=\"color:teal\">❶</span> Sound Picker. Options Include:\n            </p>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 1.2; margin: 5px 0;\">\n                <ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Drum Kit:</strong> Real drums that sound like a live rock band</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Machine:</strong> Retro electronic beats perfect for hip-hop and pop.</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Glitch:</strong> Weird, robotic drum sounds from the future.</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Cavern:</strong> Hazy, echoing drums that sound like they're in a cave.</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Glossy:</strong> Crisp, bright beats for high-energy dance party vibes.</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Gritty:</strong> Distorted, punchy drums with serious attitude.</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Underwater:</strong> Muffled, mysterious sounds for chill moods.</li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n            </p>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.2; margin: 5px 0;\">\n                <span style=\"color:teal\">❷</span> Plays the current sequence\n            </p>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.2; margin: 5px 0;\">\n                <span style=\"color:teal\">❸</span> Erases the current sequence\n            </p>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.2; margin: 5px 0;\">\n                <span style=\"color:teal\">❹</span> Instruments. Click any instrument to preview the sound.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>"
}